00:29:56.090 --> 00:29:59.903
(Shri Mataji showing the palm of her right
hand right below the vishudhi finger and the

00:29:59.903 --> 00:30:03.700
soft area below the fingers and around the
Sahastrara of the palm) I said see, these

00:30:03.700 --> 00:30:04.700
are the centers of your father.

00:30:04.700 --> 00:30:10.519
And this finger (Vishudhi) if it is so piercing
then he must be down with bad bronchitis.

00:30:10.519 --> 00:30:12.480
So he said, Really?

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:13.480
I said yes.

00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:15.769
I said, Alright! You telephone to your father
and find out.

00:30:15.769 --> 00:30:20.679
He telephoned, his mother came on the phone
and she said exactly the same sentence.

00:30:20.679 --> 00:30:24.779
“Your father is down with very bad bronchitis."

00:30:24.779 --> 00:30:26.780
So, he was amazed.

00:30:26.780 --> 00:30:31.840
Andbut then he was convinced and that’s
how he saw gradually it works.

00:30:31.840 --> 00:30:32.840
It’s fantastic.

00:30:32.840 --> 00:30:34.840
But it does happen.

00:30:34.840 --> 00:30:36.450
So the doubt starting disappearing.

00:30:36.450 --> 00:30:41.539
So then he rose to the position of doubtless
awareness.

00:30:41.539 --> 00:30:44.830
But it is not a mental activity.

00:30:44.830 --> 00:30:47.090
It is a growth within you.

00:30:47.090 --> 00:30:52.240
When that growth takes place then you have
a great power that you can give realization

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:53.419
to others.

00:30:53.419 --> 00:30:58.490
With the movement of your hand, you can give
realization.

00:30:58.490 --> 00:31:02.679
You can see what’s happening to others on
your fingertips.

00:31:02.679 --> 00:31:06.409
And you feel completely blissful.

00:31:06.409 --> 00:31:07.700
Absolutely at ease.

00:31:07.700 --> 00:31:10.500
At that point of peace where nothing can disturb
you.

00:31:10.500 --> 00:31:15.600
You are in your fortress.  You are just sitting
there and watching the whole world like a

00:31:15.600 --> 00:31:16.789
drama.

00:31:16.789 --> 00:31:18.730
It’s a big joke.

00:31:18.730 --> 00:31:23.840
It’s a big…you witness the whole thing
as just some sort of a play going on.

00:31:23.840 --> 00:31:29.440
And that is the state which comes to you which
establishes itself and you become that.

00:31:29.440 --> 00:31:34.010
Then you are no more (*UNCLEAR) or upset with
anything.

00:31:34.010 --> 00:31:36.360
As it is you are blessed.

00:31:36.360 --> 00:31:38.690
Physically, mentally, emotionally, materially
in every way.

00:31:38.690 --> 00:31:39.779
But you don’t become Mr.

00:31:39.779 --> 00:31:42.389
Ford because that’s a headache.

00:31:42.389 --> 00:31:46.510
Satisfy and your problems of material wellbeing
are solved.

