Forget it! and now you have to say with full
confidence within yourself you can ask a question

00:43:06.040 --> 00:43:07.270
to me.

00:43:07.270 --> 00:43:13.620
Addressing me as Mother if you like, or as
Shri Mataji.

00:43:13.620 --> 00:43:16.690
-Mother, am I the spirit?

00:43:16.690 --> 00:43:20.360
Ask the question thrice.

00:43:20.360 --> 00:43:38.640
If you are an indian ask the question- “kya
main atma hoon?

00:43:38.640 --> 00:43:47.770
Maa kya main atma hoon?’’ Sincerely.

00:43:47.770 --> 00:43:54.570
Now put this right hand, keep the left hand
as it is.

00:43:54.570 --> 00:43:55.600
Don’t open your eyes.

00:43:55.600 --> 00:43:59.050
Put the right hand on the stomach on left
hand side.

00:43:59.050 --> 00:44:02.970
This is the center of the primordial master.

00:44:02.970 --> 00:44:06.570
And your principle of mastery has to be awakened.

00:44:06.570 --> 00:44:16.410
