At this point- you have to assert because
if you are the spirit, you are your own master.

00:44:25.010 --> 00:44:26.570
So please say-

00:44:26.570 --> 00:44:29.220
-Mother, I am my own master.

00:44:29.220 --> 00:44:31.450
Say it ten times.

00:44:31.450 --> 00:44:36.470
With full confidence.  Don’t feel guilty
while saying that.

00:44:36.470 --> 00:44:37.470
You are.

00:44:37.470 --> 00:44:38.470
You are the spirit.

